HEADWORD: marsupiate
<hw>mar*su"pi*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Related to or resembling the marsupials; furnished with a pouch for
the young, as the marsupials, and also some fishes and
Crustacea.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

